Dr. Jerry Graham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dr._Jerry_Graham 0 Jerry Martin Graham (December 16, 1921 – January 24, 1997) was an American professional wrestler. He is best known for his time spent in the World Wide Wrestling Federation and as the founder of the Graham wrestling family.
